Title: Manually scheduling UNREACHABLE host state results in DOWN state
Component: core
Class: bug
State: done
Date: 2015-02-06 14:16:28
Targetversion: 1.2.8

The State::update() method transforms UNREACHABLE states to DOWN states
for hosts which is not correct when a user excplicit set an UNREACHABLE state

